[SHORT DESC]
10% chance to lower target's Speed by 1 stage.

[LONG DESC]
<h2>Description</h2>
<p>Deals damage and has a 10% chance to lower the target's Speed by one stage.</p>

<h2>Competitive Use</h2>
<p>Bubble is much too weak to be worthy of competitive use. BubbleBeam is 100% superior, barring PP, and even then, almost everything would prefer to use Surf or Hydro Pump due to their superior power.</p>

<h2>Related Moves</h2>
<p><a href="/bw/moves/surf">Surf</a> is a more powerful and reliable alternative with no added effect.</p>
<p><a href="/bw/moves/scald">Scald</a> is a more powerful and reliable alternative that may inflict a burn on the opponent.</p>
<p><a href="/bw/moves/hydro_pump">Hydro Pump</a> is a far more powerful alternative with lower accuracy.</p>